body:

by MystericasMercy

Tony Stark is dead.

He thought it would be worth it.

He thought he could live with himself and the sacrifice of a single man in order to save the world - or rather the entire universe. But he was wrong.

And so he had to do something.

summary: To celebrate the release of Avengers: Endgame, here is a peek at a homebrew creation from one of my games. I designed the Aegis...
caption:
To celebrate the release of Avengers: Endgame, here is a peek at a homebrew creation from one of my games. I designed the Aegis Armor for one of my players who is a massive Iron Man fan, and his character “The Iron Mage” has slowly been unlocking new upgrades and abilities for his suit. The Tier 3 & 4 upgrades have been hidden for now to avoid spoiling the surprise for my players.

Let me know what you think!

like think abt it. if he stayed alive hed be fuckin looking over his shoulder twice as much now cause he has twice the cargo to protect and hes getting old and inefficient and what if he becomes howard and yada yada
